  },
  "description": "API operations over time, across every monitored service (neutron, cinder — filter with the service variable): the report's per-type latency table as live panels. Latency percentiles are estimated from histogram buckets (labelled \"(est.)\"); true per-call min/max are not in the OTLP data, so the distribution shape is shown as a heatmap over the buckets instead. The outcome panels split failures by outcome (success / error / timeout); the \"Errors by error kind\" panel breaks them down further by error_kind (quota, http_<status>, ...) from the dedicated errors counter, empty on a healthy run. Sampling caveat: with the default continuous monitor (MONITOR_INTERVAL=0) metrics flow steadily; on a paced run they move only while an iteration runs. Panels use $__rate_interval with a 1m minimum interval.",
  "editable": true,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "victoriametrics" },
      "description": "p95 API-call latency per resource kind, estimated from histogram buckets. A bucket approximation, not a true maximum.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" }
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 1,
      "interval": "1m",
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": [], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "victoriametrics" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (kind, le) (rate(openstack_tester_operation_duration_seconds_bucket{operation=~\"$operation\", cloud=~\"$cloud\", scenario=~\"$scenario\", service=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{kind}}",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "p95 (est.) latency by kind",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "victoriametrics" },
      "description": "Mean API-call latency per resource kind, from the histogram _sum / _count ratio.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" }
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "id": 2,
      "interval": "1m",
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": [], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "victoriametrics" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by (kind) (increase(openstack_tester_operation_duration_seconds_sum{operation=~\"$operation\", cloud=~\"$cloud\", scenario=~\"$scenario\", service=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval])) / sum by (kind) (increase(openstack_tester_operation_duration_seconds_count{operation=~\"$operation\", cloud=~\"$cloud\", scenario=~\"$scenario\", service=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{kind}}",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Mean latency by kind",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "victoriametrics" },
      "description": "Distribution of API-call latency across the histogram buckets (0.05 s to 300 s). Shows the shape the percentile panels summarise.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": { "hideFrom": { "legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false }, "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" } }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "id": 3,
      "interval": "1m",
      "options": {
        "calculate": false,
        "cellGap": 1,
        "color": {
          "exponent": 0.5,
